# Icon Resources

This directory should contain application icons:

- icon.icns  - macOS icon (1024x1024, can include multiple sizes)
- icon.ico   - Windows icon (256x256, can include multiple sizes)
- icon.png   - Linux/general use (512x512)

For development, placeholder icons will be used if these files are not present.
You can create icons using online tools or image editing software.

Recommended specifications:
- macOS (.icns): 1024x1024 base size, sips or iconutil to create
- Windows (.ico): 256x256 base size, can include 16, 32, 48, 64, 128, 256
- PNG: 512x512 or 1024x1024 for high-DPI displays

